b11b178b-baf8-4c28-80db-4330a74c1d65.title: Markdown sync duplicating notes
b11b178b-baf8-4c28-80db-4330a74c1d65.description:
Renaming a task from Project Planner seems to create a new version of the Markdown note. 

This is a **high** priority issue that must be fixed for the next release.

- Created GitHub Issue
- Confirmed that task notes are being duplicated
- Confirmed that it is only the task title that causes the problem
- Renaming the task note title immediately resets back to original title. Changes have not affect.
